&lt;p&gt;As a Research Scientist II on the Fraud Research team, you will help improve how Pindrop detects, scores, and investigates fraud and scams across voice and IVR interactions. You will work on applied machine learning problems that directly impact fraud and scam prevention for major enterprise customers, balancing core model development with real-world investigation and analysis. In this role, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
